Comment: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:38.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}踊る1 2 3 steps on this dark stage
Comment: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Raise your flag, march on, fight
