Comment: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:56.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}真実は何処へ　探して
Comment: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Where's my soul? Where's my heart?
Comment: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}現実に呑まれてく
Comment: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:06.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}Don't hesitate, go this way
